                        Application
Windows                                      Mac
-> Windows Button      -> Button            -> Mac Button
-> Windows List        -> List              -> Mac List
-> Windows Text        -> Text              -> Mac Text
-> Windows list        -> dropdown list     -> Mac list

create the application and this application can
